(207, 4, 11, 'Ligo Sardines Easy Open Tomato Chili 155g 6cans', 166, NULL, 'English', NULL, NULL, 'New', NULL, NULL, 99, NULL, 'I remember when I did homestay in the mountains of Antipolo, I saw people combining sardines with instant noodles. It was an inexpensive recipe for the people there. Now that I''m living in a valley in the Philippines, I still eat sardines, particularly Ligo Sardines with tomato and chili sauce, because when I don''t want to spend time preparing and cooking food, I can just pick a can, open it using its built-in opener, pour the contents on top of steaming rice, and then, without having to cook or heat it anymore, I''m already ready to eat. ', NULL, 78, 0, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, 0),
